data.title: Gunahon Ka Devta (TV series)
data.meta_description: Gunahon Ka Devta aired from September 2010 to May 2011 on Imagine TV. The series was produced by Shyamasis Bhattacharya of Shakuntalam Telefilms. The story was set against the violent background of eastern Uttar Pradesh.
